  "original_title": "Six including 5-year old child drown",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Six including 5-year old child drown",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At least six persons including a 5-year-old child drown during three separate incidents yesterday in Polpitiya, Nawalapitiya and Hatton.",
        "Police said woman (62) and a 5-year old child who were returning home from pre-school drowned and went missing in Hitinegama, Polpitiya yesterday.",
        "The bodies of woman and the\u00a0 child - a grandmother and a granddaughter - were found during a search by police and local residents.",
        "Meanwhile, two men and a woman who went to cross the Katambulawa Oya in Akkaravatta area of \u200b\u200bNawalapitiya were suspected to have drowned and gone missing since then.",
        "The missing were aged 36, 46 and 47 are residents of Katabula area.",
        "Meanwhile, the Hatton Police have launched investigation after a man accompanied by another three men, slipped and fell into the Panmoore Lake.",
        "The police arrested the other two who were accompanying the missing man at that time under suspicion. (Darshana Sanjeewa Balasuriya)"
      ],
